d 11 uur per medewerker per week aan e-mailverwerking. Bij een uurloon van 35 euro loopt dat op tot meer dan 1.500 euro per maand per persoon, puur voor het lezen, sorteren en beantwoorden van e-mail. Autonome e-mailflows elimineren 65 tot 80 procent van dat werk."]}],"\n"]}],"\n",["$","hr","hr-0",{}],"\n",["$","h3","h3-0",{"id":"de-verborgen-kostenpost-die-niemand-bijhoudt","children":"De verborgen kostenpost die niemand bijhoudt"}],"\n",["$","p","p-0",{"children":"Vraag een ondernemer naar zijn grootste kostenposten en u hoort: personeel, huur, inkoop. Wat u zelden hoort, is e-mail. Toch is handmatige e-mailverwerking een van de grootste stille kostenvreters in het Nederlandse MKB."}],"\n",["$","p","p-1",{"children":"Het probleem is onzichtbaar omdat het versnipperd zit in de werkdag van iedereen. De salesmanager die elke ochtend een uur e-mails sorteert. De administratief medewerker die factuurvragen handmatig doorzet. De klantenservicemedewerker die twintig keer per dag hetzelfde antwoord typt. Niemand boekt dit als een aparte kostenpost, en daarom blijft het bestaan."}],"\n",["$","p","p-2",{"children":["In 2026 is dit patroon niet langer acceptabel. ",["$","strong","strong-0",{"children":"Autonome e-mailflows"}]," verwerken inkomende berichten, nemen beslissingen op basis van context, koppelen aan uw bestaande systemen en sturen het juiste antwoord, zonder dat een mens er een vinger aan hoeft te wijken."]}],"\n",["$","p","p-3",{"children":"Dit artikel berekent wat handmatige e-mailverwerking u werkelijk kost en laat zien hoe Nederlandse bedrijven dit elimineren."}],"\n",["$","hr","hr-1",{}],"\n",["$","h3","h3-1",{"id":"de-echte-kosten-een-berekening-voor-het-nederlandse-mkb","children":"De echte kosten: een berekening voor het Nederlandse MKB"}],"\n",["$","p","p-4",{"children":[["$","strong","strong-0",{"children":"De gemiddelde Nederlandse kantoormedewerker besteedt 28 procent van zijn werkweek aan e-mail."}]," Bij een 40-urige werkweek is dat ruim 11 uur per week, ofwel meer dan een volledige werkdag."]}],"\n","$L4","\n","$L5","\n","$L6","\n","$L7","\n","$L8","\n","$L9","\n","$La","\n","$Lb","\n","$Lc","\n","$Ld","\n","$Le","\n","$Lf","\n","$L10","\n","$L11","\n","$L12","\n","$L13","\n","$L14","\n","$L15","\n","$L16","\n","$L17","\n","$L18","\n","$L19","\n","$L1a","\n","$L1b","\n","$L1c","\n","$L1d","\n","$L1e","\n","$L1f","\n","$L20","\n","$L21","\n","$L22","\n","$L23","\n","$L24","\n","$L25","\n","$L26","\n","$L27","\n","$L28","\n","$L29","\n","$L2a","\n","$L2b","\n","$L2c"]}]}],"$L2d","$L2e"]}]}]}],["$L2f"],"$L30"]}],"loading":null,"isPartial":false}
